verbose_text: In prior studies by our laboratory, 6 weeks of HFD significantly increased plasma concentrations of the ketone beta-hydroxybutyrate from 4.72 +/- 0.31 in chow rats to 7.18 +/- 0.77 mg/dL in the HFD animals [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: HFD significantly increased plasma concentrations of the ketone beta-hydroxybutyrate
